nhc_headline: ...HUMBERTO FORECAST TO STRENGTHEN IN THE COMING DAYS...
summary: ...HUMBERTO FORECAST TO STRENGTHEN IN THE COMING DAYS... As of 5:00 AM AST Thu Sep 25 the center of Humberto was located near 21.2, -56.4 with movement NW at 10 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
